fields.title: Getting Started With Your First Home Page in Wagtail CMS

fields.html:
Things I like about @WagtailCMS:

1. Clean dashboard UX
2. Workflow review included
3. Solid documentation
4. Fully featured add-ons
5. Helpful community
6. Python - Django
7. Better blocks (Streamfield)
8. A CMS for developers
9. Use cloud storage for media
10. Really fast

— John ♻️ (@jtteag) May 18, 2021
